flowchart TD
    Prev([← Gate 1 passed]) --> BDD

    subgraph BDD[BDD - Behavior Driven Development]
        B1[Write Integration Tests]
        B2[Define Acceptance Criteria]
        B3[Tests FAIL 🔴]
        B4[Peer Review]
        B1 --> B2 --> B3 --> B4
    end

    BDD --> Gate2{Gate 2:<br/>Tests RED?<br/>Behavior clear?}
    Gate2 -->|No| BDD
    Gate2 -->|Yes| Next([→ TDD Phase])

    style BDD  fill:#fff3e0
    style Prev fill:#f5f5f5
    style Next fill:#f5f5f5
